life
====
A simple implementation of Conway's Game of Life.

Requirements
------------
In order to build life you need raylib library.

Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (life is installed into the
/usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install life (if
necessary as root):

    make clean install

Configuration
-------------
The configuration of life is done by creating a custom config.h and
(re)compiling the source code.
